snippet.title: ELIF Release Trailer
snippet.description: Available for free on Steam, ELIF is a puzzle platformer by the student group 6minou Production. Solve riddles, climb mountains of books and pillows, and ask for the help of your faithful companion, Crocus. http://s.team/a/1592780 #indiegames #freegames #steam
